ack on the right beside the cart, separated by the wide reflective floor. Large white on-screen graphics appear over the lower half of the image: the UPS shield logo centered above the bold words “SATURDAY DELIVERY.” Beneath that, in smaller white text, it reads, “See Air Service Guide For Guarantee Details.”",
